snippet.title: We Are Alive - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
We Are Alive is a Co-Op horror game, that can be played with at least 1 and up to 4 players. You are a detective and your mission is to investigate the old psychiatric hospital and find out the truth. Your standard equipment is a flashlight and a gun. 

Wishlist it on Steam now: We Are Alive
